{"tid":2431088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微軟指中國黑客攻擊美國　中方批評是無端猜測指責","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:47:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86437fbdcacea74d689f46ab0149af1df1e229aa","tid":2431088,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"微軟指中國黑客攻擊美國　中方批評是無端猜測指責<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578544-20210303.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578544-20210303.htm&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=b168dab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578544-20210303.htm&h=50c67ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578544-20210303.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國微軟公司表示，中國政府支持的黑客利用電子郵件伺服器當中的漏洞來攻擊美國的組織，黑客又一直試圖竊取大學、律師事務所及傳染病研究員的信息。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應說，中國堅決反對並依法打擊任何形式的網絡攻擊和網絡竊密行為，這個立場是一貫和明確的。中方多次重申，網絡空間具有虛擬性強，溯源難，行為體多樣的特點，網絡攻擊溯源是複雜的技術問題。將網絡攻擊直接與政府相關聯，更是高度敏感的政治問題。中方希望有關媒體和企業採取專業和負責任的態度，在定性網絡事件的時候基於充分證據，而不是無端猜測指責。"},{"pid":"948cc346a7d44e293b9e75d3d1bd5693620144d7","tid":2431088,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"Microsoft佢做乜忽然咁誠實"},{"pid":"000ba7b41b5756da4861ae7c38f9675142e7d2fd","tid":2431088,"uid":67065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"玩c&amp;c 用黑客搵錢係咩國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011581f6253b764b1a479d7ea81686fcc8b3a7d8","tid":2431088,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbc7d11ce8676910812bd8f52e21d8c0d61078b","tid":2431088,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-0